description:
Don't let nighttime teeth grinding steal your smile! Sleep better knowing your teeth are protected from bruxism with the DenTek Maximum Protection Dental Guard. The only over-the-counter dental guard with a forming tray, it creates a superior fit similar to professionally made dental guards, but without the professional expense.

- Custom Form Your Own Guard

- Perfect Fit

- Comfortable Protection

- BPA & Latex Free

- Fits Upper Teeth
title: Dentek® Maximum Protection Dental Guard

bullets: Offers custom-fit protection similar to a professionally made mouth guard—for a fraction of the cost
All bite guard parts are BPA-free and latex-free
Helps prevent conditions caused by teeth grinding (bruxism), including jaw discomfort, tooth chipping and cracking, and headaches
soft_bullets.title: highlights

description: The Extra Comfort Night Guard from up & up helps protect your teeth from damage caused from teeth grinding. The custom-fit design molds to your mouth in minutes, providing comfortable protection all night. This pack of two makes it easy to keep a clean mouthguard on hand.
title: Night Guard - 2ct - up & up™

bullets: Nighttime mouthguard helps prevent tooth grinding
Custom-fit dental guard molds to your mouth in minutes
Pack of 2 teeth-grinding guards lets you always have one on hand

description: The SleepRight® Ultra-Comfort® Dental Guard prevents teeth from grinding, clenching and gnashing while sleeping. Four notches let you adjust the bite pads forward or backward for a custom fit. This low-profile mouth guard also swivels to match your bite angles. A flexible, heat-sensitive band conveniently fits between your lower lip, teeth and gums. It uses your body's temperature to quickly conform for a perfect fit. This dental night guard stays in place by using the natural tissue retention between your lips and tongue. Includes a travel case for added convenience.
title: Sleep Right Slim Comfort Dental Guard

bullets: Adjustable night guard protects your teeth from clenching and grinding
Does not require boiling water and biting hot plastic for fitting
Protects 4x longer than leading competitors based on a lab study
Slim design eliminates bulkier night guards
4 notches allow you to adjust the bite pads forward and backward to fit all sizes
soft_bullets.title: highlights

Eliminates bulkier night guards, fits braces and dentures
4 notches allow you to adjust the bite-pads forward and backward
Designed for adults with small mouths, a low-profile bite, sensitive gums or to be worn during the day

description: So comfortable, you’ll forget you’re wearing them! Plackers Grind No More Dental Night Protectors are specifically designed for night time teeth grinding (bruxism). Made from light weight material and free of sharp edges and other uncomfortable features, these dental night guards are barely visible. Unlike boil-to-fit type night guards, Plackers Grind No More protectors do not require forming or adjusting – one size fits all!
title: Plackers Grind No More Dental Night Protector - 10ct

bullets: 10 count
Advanced protection against night time teeth grinding
No boiling necessary – one size fits all
The streamlined one size fits all is designed to be worn on upper or lower teeth – whichever is more comfortable
BPA Free

description: The Ora-GUARD® Maximum Protection Dental Grind Guard features a Patented Bite Plate Wedge Design, and medical grade fit material, which slides the lower jaw down and forward.  It provides protection and helps reduce effects of nighttime teeth grinding, bruxism, and jaw clenching.    It is intended to reduce damage to teeth and prevent the noise associated with teeth grinding and bruxism.  Intended to be worn while sleeping (e.g., at night or while napping).  Comfortable "Fit-Tight" Design that Ends Sleep Interrupting Grinding Noise.  Easy 60 seconds microwave to fit.  Includes a dental grind guard and storage case.
title: Ora-GUARD Dental Grind Guard

bullets: Easy 60 seconds microwave to fit

Features medical grade fit material that cushions and absorbs tension, and a patented Bite Plate wedge design that slides the jaw down and forward, reducing the effects of teeth grinding and jaw clenching
Includes dental grind guard and storage case

This dental guard includes an adjustable band, cushioned bite pads and comfort bumpers that are soft on your gums and cheeks.

description: GrindReliefN is the best guard for people who clench and grind thier teeth at night. GrindReliefN beings the preformace you would expect at the dentist office at an over the counter price. The unique central power bar reduces biting forces by up to 60% or more. GrindReliefN is much smaller than other over the counter devices, and can be fitted to the upper or lower teeth. Find relief today from problems related to clenching and grinding with GrindReliefN.
